 -- Michael Koehne <kraehe@copyleft.de> 07 Aug 2002

CGI::pWiki 0.14
  
  * pWiki.cgi is now a ErrorDocument 404 handler, for old apaches
  * search in a notfound document
  * parse_request will also parse post data
  * save does no longer parse post data
  * error might be an assignment

 -- Michael Koehne <kraehe@copyleft.de> 03 Aug 2002

CGI::pWiki 0.13

  * CGI::pWiki is now pod and a bit more
  * the <wiki tags are converted to pod command paragraphs
  * the menu bar is now called content and not index
  * autolinks are now in brackets and not in percents
  * title and body extraction from html files

 -- Michael Koehne <kraehe@copyleft.de> 01 Aug 2002

